lead_paragraph: Bayern Munich ended a three-match winless run when they beat Bayer Leverkusen 2-1 on Saturday, although the Bundesliga champions still had to cling on at the end.

headline.print_headline: Bayern End Winless Streak, Hoffenheim Still Unbeaten
